# Account Management Tools
# These tools are defined inline in the agent DSL files.
# This file serves as a tool registry reference for the v2 export format.

# Tools:
#   verify_identity — Verify customer identity via email, phone, or security questions
#   reset_password — Initiate password reset via email or phone verification
#   check_icloud_status — Check iCloud storage usage, plan, and connected devices
#   manage_two_factor — Enable, disable, or generate recovery key for 2FA
#   unlock_apple_id — Attempt to unlock a locked Apple ID
